📘 Protocol Spec
https://www.w3.org/Protocols/rfc2616/rfc2616.html

The core spec. Focus especially on sections 4 (Requests), 6 (Responses), 9 (Methods).

💡 Reference Implementations

https://github.com/nodejs/http-parser

Lightweight, performant C implementation. 
Great to understand state machine parsing.(Node.js HTTP Parser)

https://github.com/apache/httpd

Massive, but shows how parsing and response generation is separated. (Appache)

📚 Extras

Mozilla Developer Docs - HTTP Overview (We can discus which of the browsers to support)

https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP

Excellent high-level explanations for planning headers, status codes, request anatomy.